BREAKING: Roma president James Pallotta: &quot;Nainggolan will go to Inter&quot; &quot;Alisson is close to joining Real Madrid&quot;<br />
<br />
James Pallotta has just revealed massive transfer market news regarding Inter and Nainggolan. The Roma president speaks about Alisson and the Belgian midfielder, two prized elements of his team that could leave this summer. When asked whether he will give up either one of them to Napoli, Pallotta said that &ldquo;no, De Laurentiis does not want to spend all this money. Alisson costs a lot, 78 million is needed and he is close to Real Madrid. Meanwhile, Nainggolan will go to Inter.&rdquo;

